{"tid":2355302,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唯一反對派鄭松泰做咩又唔投票呀？","createTime":"2021-01-06T04:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T04:04:55.000Z","uid":7439,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd1a49fd4f90cf3119131456e30671c9303f94d","tid":2355302,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:47:56.000Z","msg":"掛住幸災樂禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080027&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=2899fe8d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1080027&h=d0245052\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1080027</a><br />\n（獨媒報導）立法會工務小組今早復會舉行會議，審議在加路連山道用地興建地區康健中心，該項目造價為1億6,800萬元項目。在討論近半小時，主席謝偉銓宣佈舉手表決，最終在工聯會麥美娟、何君堯及經民聯盧偉國贊成、無人反對下極速通過項目。<br />\n<br />\n中標的發展商需負責灣仔康健中心的設計、興建、裝修和粉飾工程，完成後移交政府作為政府物業，由食物及衞生局管理，政府則會向地產商發還設施的實際建築費用。鄭松泰批評發展模式不理想，擔心康健中心質素參差，「依家好多商廈連牆紙喺香港都搵唔返」，要求加強工程條款，保障中心質素。葉青雲強調在賣地條款中會列明康建中心的要求及規格，如不達標政府將不會付款。<br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/50805644262_f8df271376_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F50805644262_f8df271376_z.jpg&h=8ca04c00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr20-21/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/pwsc20210106.htm#s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr20-21%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fresults%2Fpwsc20210106.htm%23s&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=5ca213e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr20-21/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/pwsc20210106.htm#s</a><br />\n投都唔洗投<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f633f3fe3e6ac14acd63f3b1e52a2614ab8f7b79","tid":2355302,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:48:07.000Z","msg":"謝偉俊：鄭松泰說他完全不相信數據保安，不知道他是否因此而沒膽量參加初選<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2172024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2172024</a>"},{"pid":"5c3cc9bb72db8020ccba300f5085ef620f69dfe0","tid":2355302,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:48:44.000Z","msg":"11 : 1又係到打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰最尾一秒投唯一反對票都要吹奏自己..........<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2328385\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2328385</a>"},{"pid":"a34bd38cb77d97f4f3c1c6dc7715f60320713a54","tid":2355302,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:51:07.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰：我一點也不喜歡政治，我午餐通常選擇吃齋菜。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2297035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2297035</a><br />\n鄭松泰：其實我是一名本土自由派<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2282932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2282932</a><br />\n鄭松泰：希望大家不要將我標籤為建制派，要講道理OK？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2263918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2263918</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰憂慮《国安法》下法官判決會被視為違反誓言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2348908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2348908</a><br />\n鄭松泰憂慮《国安法》下終審法院判決亦可被推翻<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2192649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2192649</a><br />\n国安法：無需陪審團<br />\n熱狗：挽回司法公正，建議區院引入陪審團<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2096511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2096511</a>"},{"pid":"4048d722d61b895e8098eb386236ba4a5bb6df6a","tid":2355302,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主可唔可以唔好再貼熱狗d post,好撚督眼督鼻<br />\n我四年前投左佢已經好後悔，唔好